>\n<br />\n香港人，係時候要報恩<br />\n612就係全靠呢班人，如果唔係送中惡法已經過咗😭<br />\n<br />\n要我哋行三個鐘頭入去救佢哋我都願意😭<br />\n<br />\n中大守得住， 香港先有希望守得住"},{"pid":"1536e1252a47c3cb4cad9805df17afb47715e6dd","tid":1713243,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣絕對需要set rb 11-13<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad11c11510b2e5f0fc59e5357b61f161af227326","tid":1713243,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:30:03.000Z","msg":"聽日都要罷啊，各位"},{"pid":"23711b511ef1d16672c58f28211fc8d8cbad101e","tid":1713243,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}